#: ../../docs/classes/class_planemesh.rst:19
msgid ""
"Class representing a planar :ref:`PrimitiveMesh <class_PrimitiveMesh>`. "
"This flat mesh does not have a thickness. By default, this mesh is "
"aligned on the X and Z axes; this default rotation isn't suited for use "
"with billboarded materials. For billboarded materials, use :ref:`QuadMesh"
" <class_QuadMesh>` instead."
